_sText:
GG_ZT-q3dm6 - is remake of Quake 3 map pro-q3dm6.
Its not exact copy.
Build time - 5 days.
Not very detailed, but simple.
Contain - 20x20 player spawns (40 in total).
Custom textures.
Mega health with sound =), well its not +100 hp, but +50 to current and not past 100 hp. Respawns every 30 second.
